Package com.example.Game.model

Class Cell

java.lang.Object
com.example.Game.model.Cell
public class Cell extends Object
The Grid class contains the Cell grid upon which the GameLogic operates on. Data included is a 10x10 grid of Cells. Function responsibilities return the status of individual cells based on a given set of x and y coordinates.
